put.description:
# Device

Update an existing Device (e.g. a DVR camera).

| Parameter               | Description                   |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| id                      | GUID of the Device to Update. |

# Request

```
{
    "ManufactureIdentifier": [int] Device Foreign Id,
    "Description": "Device Name",
    "DeviceTypeListItem": {
      "Guid": "GUID of Device Type -- See Device Type API"
    },
    "DeviceStatusListItem": {
      "Guid": "GUID of Device Status -- See Device Status API"
    }
}
```

post.description:
# Device

Create a new Device (e.g. a DVR camera).

# Request

```
{
    "ManufactureIdentifier": [int] Device Foreign Id,
    "Description": "Device Name",
    "DeviceTypeListItem": {
      "Guid": "GUID of Device Type -- See Device Type API"
    },
    "DeviceStatusListItem": {
      "Guid": "GUID of Device Status -- See Device Status API"
    }
}
```

# Response

```
{
    "resource": "GUID of newly created Device"
}
```

get.description:
# Device Status

Request possible statuses a Device can have.

| Property                | Description                                     |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| GUID                    | GUID associated to the DeviceStatus         |
| Description             | Descriptive Name of the DeviceStatus        |

# Response

```
{
    "resource": [
        {
            "resource": {
                "Description": "Name of DeviceStatus",
                "IsDeleted": true/false,
                "GUID": "GUID of DeviceStatus"
            }
        },
        ...
    ]
}
```

